column2: An eldritch force makes it hard to swim.

The portal to your right will take you to Boss Rush.
You'll face every main boss consecutively, in general order of difficulty.
Your wands, perks, and items will be left here.
Taking too much damage will force you to leave Boss Rush, but don't worry!
You get unlimited attempts, and you won't take any real damage or die.
Good luck, adventurer!
The portal to your left will take you back.
